{"tid":514803,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬：應獲判12碼","createTime":"2017-12-30T23:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T23:46:01.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22400085f21bf811980d6de8bf7162387a30e671","tid":514803,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T23:24:12.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=sORSVQCKdiD82CoCnWMROTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=76251248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯在周六英超主場僅跟修咸頓踢成0:0，領隊摩連奴賽後表示，他們理應獲得12碼。<br />\n<br />\n上半場，修咸頓中堅吉田麻也在禁區犯手球，球證包臣未有判12碼，摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）顯然非常不滿：「我們錯失了數個容易的入球機會，但我真的為那球12碼感到不高興，但不是怪責包臣。」<br />\n<br />\n摩佬又指，雖然再失2分，但仍然很滿意球員的鬥心：「我為球員的作戰態度感到愉快，他們有爭勝的欲望。」<br />\n<br />\n至於紅魔中場保羅普巴（Paul Pogba）也認為應該獲得12碼：「我們很想贏，最終只得和局，一定要重拾勝利的心態。我們今場處理最後一傳不太好，而且有一球12碼沒有獲判，若果我們射入了這12碼，比賽將會完全不同。」"},{"pid":"338bab321118a30fa1794f1ab5b83440325be7cb","tid":514803,"uid":90726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T23:25:53.000Z","msg":"曼聯打小4個唔公平呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07875472ef7e9667b987bfbd1333a9ec835ccc1f","tid":514803,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T23:28:02.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"fe2e94efca9d8686b9f2c3b8510455272ecd2474","tid":514803,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"741a688ac6b59e7c3c0e8d12e97a09f90f99902e","tid":514803,"uid":48104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"全世界都逼害我曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}